        "body": "Summary\r\nThis PR enhances engine downloads by introducing a fallback mechanism from custom mirrors to the official Prisma CDN if the mirror download fails.\r\nWe introduce a new environment variable, PRISMA_ENGINES_STRICT_MIRROR, to disable this fallback and enforce strict mirror usage. This variable is now surfaced in $ prisma debug.\r\n\r\nTesting\r\n- pnpm --filter @prisma/fetch-engine test download\r\n- pnpm --filter prisma test -- DebugInfo",
